text = "Comments are non-executable text used for internal documentation. They are stripped away during the compilation process and do not appear in the bytecode. Java provides three types of comment syntax:

* Single-line (`//`): Terminates at the end of the line.

* Multi-line/Block (`/* ... */`): Encloses any amount of text, spanning multiple lines if necessary.

* Documentation/Javadoc (`/** ... */`): A specialized block comment used by the `javadoc` tool to generate professional HTML-based API documentation."
autowrap_mode = 2

